{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2515","id":3711581773,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEHbxG87dOj5N","html_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2515","diff_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2515.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2515.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2515","number":2515,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"lb: improve lbcollision capsule-collision matching","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime","html_url":"https://github.com/itsgrimetime","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/itsgrimetime/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"Match work on `lbcollision.c`. Named some fields I was pretty confident about, but will likely still need some work as the big ones get closer to 100%\r\n\r\n## New 100% matches\r\n\r\n| Function | Before | After |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| `lbColl_8000A244` | 99.9% | 100% |\r\n| `lbColl_8000A78C` | 99.9% | 100% |\r\n| `lbColl_8000A95C` | 99.9% | 100% |\r\n| `lbColl_8000AB2C` | 99.9% | 100% |\r\n\r\n## Improved (still <100%)\r\n\r\n| Function | Before | After |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| `lbColl_80006094` | 78.7% | 91.4% |\r\n| `lbColl_800067F8` | 78.7% | 89.4% |\r\n| `lbColl_80006E58` | 81.0% | 95.4% |\r\n| `lbColl_8000A584` | 99.7% | 99.8% |\r\n\r\n## Code changes\r\n\r\n> - `lbColl_80006E58`: name parameters by role (`hit_start`/`hit_end`, `hurt_start`/`hurt_end`, `hit_closest`/`hurt_closest`, `hurt_mtx`, `out_contact_pos`, `out_overlap`, `hit_radius`/`hurt_radius`, `broadphase_scale`).\r\n> - Drop `lbColl_JObjGetMtxPtr` and its two `lbColl_804D37*` assert strings; no longer referenced.\r\n> - Collapse `float xx_x/_y/_z` triplets into `Vec3 xx` in `lbColl_80005C44` and the parallel-axes branches of > `lbColl_80006E58`.\r\n> - Fold `hit_param = (hit_param_candidate = ...)` into an assignment expression in the closest-points solve.\r\n> - Cache `1.0` in a callee-save float to avoid reloading it across `*_param = 1.0` branches in `lbColl_80006E58`.\r\n> The three remaining sub-100% functions still have residual float-register-allocation mismatches.","created_at":"2026-05-19T19:52:34Z","updated_at":"2026-05-19T21:57:50Z","closed_at":"2026-05-19T21:57:50Z","merged_at":"2026-05-19T21:57:50Z","merge_commit_sha":"0030f76087853d182706ad07aaab2f5f66162e0b","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2515/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2515/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2515/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/dbf93fa9d9371944069f2be4342882138d76b3bd","head":{"label":"itsgrimetime:pr/lb-collision-3d-capsule","ref":"pr/lb-collision-3d-capsule","sha":"dbf93fa9d9371944069f2be4342882138d76b3bd","user":{"login":"itsgrimetime","id":990274,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk5MDI3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/990274?v=4","gravatar_id":"",